                    </list>
                    
                    y-inta <choice><sic>śe</sic><corr>peru</corr></choice> nāṅk’ el<choice><orig>k</orig><reg>l</reg></choice>aik
                    <pb n="1v"/>
                    <lb n="1v1=31"/>k’ uḷpaṭa kaḷakkuṭiki<hi rend="grantha">śa</hi>mam caṟvamāṇiyam
                    <lb n="1v2=32" break="no"/>-āka tāṉam paṇṇi kuṭuttōm Ācantirākka 
                    <lb n="1v3=33" break="no"/>t=tāyiyāka y-āṉṟu Āṉupavittu-k koḷḷuv 
                    <lb n="1v4=34"/>ā=r<surplus>=ā r=</surplus>ākavu=M
                </p>   
                
                <p> 
