                    <lb n="1v5=35" break="no"/>ṉavarkaḷukku keṅkai-k-karaiyilum Āti ⌈
                    <lb n="1v6=36" break="no"/>cētuvilu=M Āyiram civaliṅka-pi<choice><sic>e</sic><corr>ra</corr></choice>tiṭ⌈
                    <lb n="1v7=37" break="no"/>ṭaiyum Āyiram kō-tāṉam paṇṇiṉa pala
                    <lb n="1v8=38" break="no"/>ṉai Aṭaivār= ākavu=M
                </p>
                <p>
                    y-inta taṟmattukku y
                    <lb n="1v9=39" break="no"/>ātāmoruvar Akutam niṉaittavarkaḷukku
                    <lb n="1v10=40"/>keṅkai-k-karaiyilum Āti-cētuvilum
